description: Pilipinas Taj Autogroup Inc. recently introduced its newest commercial vehicle lineup in the Philippines in an event held at SMX Convention Center, Pasay City. The new lineup includes the Tata Prima Range of Tractor Trailers and Tippers, the LPT Range of Light, Medium, and Heavy Trucks, SFC 407, and the Mini Trucks range of Ace and SuperAce.  It was in 2014 when Tata Motors came to the Philippine shores initially to bring in their passenger cars like the Indigo and the Manza. This time around they are ready to get a share in the trucking sector offering commercial vehicles in uplifting the country‚Äôs logistic and business trade market.   Also during the launch, Pilipinas Taj Autogroup awarded plaque of appreciation to their loyal consumers and dealers.
